cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea5' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and prevent secure communication establishment.

du.explanation_en: Setting the RF simulator model name to an unsupported value 'INVALID_MODEL' will cause initialization failures in the RF simulation module and prevent DU startup.
du.explanation_zh: 將 RF 模擬器模型名稱設定為不支援的值 'INVALID_MODEL'，會導致 RF 模擬模組初始化失敗，並阻止 DU 啟動。
